Output demos/shots/_help.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 36
Set Width 1920
Set Height 1180
Set Padding 20
Set Margin 0
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 30ms

Hide
Type "UNRAGER_DISABLE_KITTY=1 ./target/release/unrager"
Enter
Sleep 7s
Show
Sleep 1s
Type "?"
Sleep 1500ms
Screenshot demos/shots/help.png
Space
Sleep 400ms
Type "q"
Sleep 200ms
